"Thank You for your Registration. To Complete the Registration Process and Activate your Account, you Must Verify your E-mail Address. Click on the Link Below to Confirm your E-mail and you Will be Automatically Logged Into your New Account.\n"
"\n"
"http://127.0.0.1:8000/%(language)s?verification-code=%(verification_code)s&id=%(id)s\n"
"\n"
"This Link is Valid for the Next 24 hours. After this Time, you Will Need to Register Again for Security Reasons. If you Did Not Register, Please Ignore this E-mail.\n"
"Street Workout Žilina Team."

